description: Provides information about a given change set.

parameters.name: Catalog
parameters.description: Required. The catalog related to the request. Fixed value: AWSMarketplace.

parameters.name: ChangeSetId
parameters.description: Required. The unique identifier for the StartChangeSet request that you want to describe the details for.

nested_items.name: ChangeSetId
nested_items.description: Required. The unique identifier for the change set referenced in this request.

nested_items.name: ChangeSetArn
nested_items.description: The ARN associated with the unique identifier for the change set referenced in this request.

nested_items.name: ChangeSetName
nested_items.description: The optional name provided in the StartChangeSet request. If you do not provide a name, one is set by default.

nested_items.name: Intent
nested_items.description: The optional intent provided in the StartChangeSet request. If you do not provide an intent, APPLY is set by default.

nested_items.name: StartTime
nested_items.description: The date and time, in ISO 8601 format (2018-02-27T13:45:22Z), the request started.

nested_items.name: EndTime
nested_items.description: The date and time, in ISO 8601 format (2018-02-27T13:45:22Z), the request transitioned to a terminal state. The change cannot transition to a different state. Null if the request is not in a terminal state.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The status of the change request.

nested_items.name: FailureCode
nested_items.description: Returned if the change set is in FAILED status. Can be either CLIENT_ERROR, which means that there are issues with the request (see the ErrorDetailList), or SERVER_FAULT, which means that there is a problem in the system, and you should retry your request.

nested_items.name: FailureDescription
nested_items.description: Returned if there is a failure on the change set, but that failure is not related to any of the changes in the request.

nested_items.name: Details
nested_items.description: This object contains details specific to the change type of the requested change.

nested_items.name: DetailsDocument
nested_items.description: The JSON value of the details specific to the change type of the requested change.

nested_items.name: ErrorDetailList
nested_items.description: An array of ErrorDetail objects associated with the change.

nested_items.name: ErrorCode
nested_items.description: The error code that identifies the type of error.
